README
======

What is Solidocs?
----------------

Solidocs is a PHP MVC framework. Solidocs is a very light and works right out
of the box. The word "Solidocs" is a combination of Solid + Docs (documents).

Solidocs comes bundled with the Admin, Node, Dynamic and CLEditor packages,
when combined you get a solid content management system.

Requirements
------------

PHP 5.2
MySQL 5.1

Documentation
-------------

There is not yet any documentation available for Solidocs. Documentation will
be available at http://solidocs.com when Solidocs 1.0 is publicly released.
Until then you can follow solidocs at Twitter: http://twitter.com/solidocs